{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act44side", "eventName": "墟", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AT-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "極道作風", "storyInfo": "御機的刑警惟任認為星熊應對二十年前的一場命案負責，但這件案子的追訴期已經過了，星熊回御機也只是因為情同養父的黑道——金石會會長鐵齋的一封信。警察一籌莫展之際，金石會的三船光平找上警局，把星熊保了出來。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刑警，炸肉排飯到了。", "name": "值班警察"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦了。你先回去吧。", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！", "name": "值班警察"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經半夜了，你從下午進入御機就在躲我們的人，連口飯都沒得吃，一定餓了吧。", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（點頭）", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那先吃飯吧。東國的炸肉排飯。", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plateplace", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刑警特地強調了“東國”兩個字，把餐盤推給星熊。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pickupchopsticks", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊一言不發地拿起深碗，抓起筷子，開始大口扒飯。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "64_i01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "x": 150.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 60.0, "xTo": 0.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣，龍門有這種東西嗎？", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dishes", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（悶頭扒飯）", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你這副樣子，到底有多長時間沒吃過家鄉菜了？", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（往嘴裡塞肉排）", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了，你先吃。", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humaneat", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（咯吱咯吱地嚼高麗菜）", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（喝水）", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dishes", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（把整個深碗端起來仰頭往嘴裡扒）", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 2.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plateplace", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（放下空空如也的深碗）", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣，懷念嗎？", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告刑警，不是懷念，我就只是餓了。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我從龍門出發前就吃過炸肉排飯了。下次能請我吃別的嗎？比如你們把我抓走那個地方的關東煮？聞起來那麼香，我都來不及喝一口湯。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，順帶一提，我在龍門自掏腰包請嫌疑人吃飯的時候都是吃腸粉的。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我放尊重點，星熊嫌疑人。", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嫌疑人？我才來御機不到二十四小時，我的嫌疑是什麼？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年前的嫌疑人就不是嫌疑人了嗎？", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……刑警先生。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我姓惟任。", "name": "刑警"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "惟任刑警。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說。", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年，我的追訴期已經過了。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，我在龍門的督察證現在也應該確認得差不多了吧。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果還沒出來。", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假設你說的是真的好了，那到底是什麼風，能把一位龍門警察吹回來？", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你失業了？你有仇家要對付？", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "龍門有什麼人派你來的？", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，你跟最近城裡在傳的北院間諜有關係？", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停停停，你再這樣繼續猜下去，事情就大條了。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刑警，看看這封信吧。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛已經搜過一遍，你身上竟然還藏著東西？", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警察最懂警察。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lungmenbridge", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$motorbikestart", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 45.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$drift", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 25.0, "randomness": 45.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再跑一圈，怎麼樣，兄弟，還撐得住嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 45.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$motorbikestart", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來還可以。那就走吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#11$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$motorbikestart"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_enginerun", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（是夫人的車？）", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$motorbikestart"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獨角的鬼把整個身體趴在車上，看準了直線路段結束的位置，筆直地朝前衝去。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咆哮的風幾乎讓她看不清追趕者的距離——"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$drift", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夫人怎麼停車了？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來湊個熱鬧而已，沒打算一決高下。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽彥吾說，出發去新汐斯塔前，詩懷雅將局內事務打理得井井有條，免得讓你們這些留守的增添壓力。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊。要不是Missy臨走前把事情處理得乾淨俐落，沒有留什麼負擔給我，我怎麼能抽出時間來這裡呢。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是。那還有什麼事能讓星熊督察煩心？", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……難道都寫在我的臉上了？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也沒有。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，若是一直反覆將油門踩到底，心情卻總也無法平復，那就不該一個人憋著。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偏偏小陳和詩懷雅都不在，只好由我這個同鄉來越俎代庖了。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同鄉……是嗎？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，同鄉。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是瞞不過夫人。我最近收到了一封信……", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "拜啟", "x": 200.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "時值夏末，殘暑尚在，切盼珍重身體。二十年久疏問候，此間情狀種種，信以不寫為佳，然仍提筆叨擾，實在不勝慚愧。", "multi": "true", "x": 200.0, "y": 260.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "\\n此次寫信，非為別事，特因你我共度十數年之故土，鍛冶町，即將不存於世。", "x": 300.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "left", "multi": "true", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "\\n地雖無知，人猶有情，是以不揣鄙陋，竊為鍛冶町舉喪，不日即將實行。", "x": 300.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "left", "multi": "true", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "\\n老朽風燭殘年，若屆時能得見故人一面，實乃大幸。", "x": 300.0, "y": 380.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "multi": "true", "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "敬具", "x": 200.0, "y": 500.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "multi": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "\\n鐵齋", "x": 200.0, "y": 510.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 900.0, "multi": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好鄭重的——不，守舊的寫法。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位就是當年安排星熊督察來龍門避禍的，般若的“父親”？", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，我叫他鐵齋叔。這麼多年過去，他應該也七八十歲了。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而鍛冶町，就是我離開御機之前住的地方。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，在鍛冶町“即將不存”的時候回去一趟，難道不是應有之義？", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……老實說，當年我來龍門時，想過在這裡長居，想過混不下去之後去其他地方，甚至像離開東國一樣離開大炎，唯獨沒想過回去。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年過去，我都不知道御機現在變成什麼樣子了，比起回去，不如來這裡騎車，結束之後再去路邊吃一盤炒米粉還比較安心。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理由不是已經有了嗎？一場葬禮，剛好可以回家看看。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自願成為龍門最堅固的盾，為此奮不顧身，彥吾、我、林，還有你那些朋友們，我們都看在眼裡。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你本不應局限於此。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小陳走了，雨霞八成會接她父親的班。只靠一個近衛局局長，這樣是做不起來的。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我對自己的職務多有怠慢——", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼說。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小陳離開龍門之前，你跟她說過一些話。不管我願意還是不願意，這些話終究會傳到我的耳朵裡。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕你壓抑著的那些東西已經永遠不能解決，就算只是回去看看，去和尚在人世的人聊一聊，總歸也是好的。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，回來時記得帶幾包東國的甜醬油煎餅給我。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煎餅？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1645_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "近衛局附近新開了一家煎餅店，我以為是東國風味，就去店裡點來吃。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到熱騰騰的煎餅裹著香噴噴的羽獸卵液、炸肉和蔥段端上來，我才意識到，這個煎餅不是東國的，是姜齊的。", "name": "文月"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想現在誤會應該都解除了吧，惟任刑警。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑道組織“金石會”的會長寫了封信給你，讓你參加他盤踞的鍛冶町的葬禮。在你同鄉的勸說下，你下定決心回來，是這樣嗎？", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位同鄉——", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是誰不重要。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不重要嗎？如果不是你的那位好同鄉，你真的敢大搖大擺地出現在御機街上？", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然敢。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然不重要，那你就在這裡待滿二十四小時再走。", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正警局現在也沒事，每天打來的報警電話也沒幾個是真的有問題。", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他們幹嘛打電話？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告自己發現了怪談的線索，讓我們過去調查清楚。", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……怪談？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，看來你真的有很多年沒回過御機了。", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警察局現在根本沒有警察局的樣子，那些無聊人士早就把我們當成了靈務局——", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外面有人找，是……三船先生。", "name": "值班警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一臉勞碌相的刑警看看星熊，又看了看門外，臉上露出明顯的憤恨。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是您這邊正在緊要關頭，我去幫您拖一下？", "name": "值班警察"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你拖得住他？你還沒跟他說三句話，他就會打電話給別人，然後電話就會打到我們這裡。", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "值班警察"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫他進——", "name": "惟任刑警"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刑警的話還沒說完，一位身材高大的斐迪亞已經大步走進房間，對身旁的警察視若無睹，直接來到了星熊身旁。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金兵衛？！", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#9$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊，別擔心，有我在這裡，警察奈何不了你。", "name": "金兵衛？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（乾笑）哈、哈哈。三船光平先生，有人叫你發跡之前的原名，是不是也很久違了？", "name": "惟任刑警"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1898_1#3$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "惟任刑警，不如你也來叫一聲如何？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "惟任刑警"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1898_1#2$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，識時務是好事。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊，在你面前，我永遠都是金兵衛。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走，我們現在就回家。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "惟任先生還沒——", "name": "值班警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒什麼？還沒跟我講清楚，警察有什麼權力亂抓人嗎？難道是為了二十年前的那起案子？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不巧，追訴期已經過了，而且過了好幾年。北院修改了追訴制度，不代表南院的警察也可以學他們肆意妄為。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少在這裡血口噴人，哪怕過了追訴期——", "name": "值班警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過了追訴期，警察還有什麼資格把人扣留在這裡？給我一個理由，經得起議員質詢、電視直播、民意拷問的理由。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是恐嚇！", "name": "值班警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我行使權利的方式。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "惟任先生！", "name": "值班警察"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1915_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……放他們走。", "name": "惟任刑警"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1898_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……金兵衛，是鐵齋叔派你來接我的嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個金石會都在等你回來呢。走吧，別再跟這些警察耗下去了。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.8, "delay": 0.15, "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_sunshine_upperedge", "layer": 2.0, "x": 0.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g1_jindastreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 45.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走出警局，出門右轉，過一條街。"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白天的仁田街赫然出現在星熊面前。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無機質的白色日光平淡地灑滿整條街道，混凝土的建築外牆失去霓虹的輝映，現出原本的顏色。"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是上班時分，面無表情的上班族們行色匆匆，經過要嘛還沒開業，要嘛仍在攬客，卻已經失去了夜色中的光鮮的大小商店。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨晚是誰在街頭大吐特吐，又是誰在勸誘下一擲千金，此刻早已無法分辨。"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.25}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g1_jindastreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好幾年沒見到你了！你在龍門怎麼樣，還好嗎？這麼多年音訊不通，我真的很怕你在那邊出了什麼事，我都快擔心死了！", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為這麼多年過去，自己已經不算金石會的人了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼話啊。哪怕命運捉弄，音訊不通，只要你回來，就是我們的家人。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年來，金石會有發過任何將你“破門”或者“絕緣”的公告嗎？從來沒有。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別的不說，直到現在，開大會的時候，老爺子左手邊位置一直都是空著的。你一直是整個金石會的若頭。接班人。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你……？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若頭補佐而已。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千萬別覺得老爺子糊塗。他這麼做，所有人都是服氣的。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年前，如果不是你挺身而出，搶在我前面殺死了那位議員候選人，整個金石會都會被趕出鍛冶町，在他的輿論攻勢之下粉身碎骨。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，你又把我們這些人排除在外，自己一個人擔負了殺人的重責，遠遁龍門，才讓金石會得以存續。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為我們做出了這麼大的犧牲，要是我們一轉頭就拋棄你，那我們還算是人嗎？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……別這麼說。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這都是清清楚楚的事實，我怎麼能不這麼說？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金兵衛，舊事可以等一下再聊。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐵齋叔在信上說他要幫鍛冶町舉辦葬禮，這件事，他跟你說過嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葬禮？！", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#5$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葬禮……不，那怎麼會是一場葬禮呢？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬼姐，現在我們真的沒時間在街上東遊西逛了。我們快點回鍛冶町，快點找到他，把事情講清楚。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高大的斐迪亞加快了腳步，急匆匆地朝著鍛冶町的方向走去。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他步子邁得那麼大，那麼急，以至於星熊不得不小跑著追上去。"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}